<h2>About Us</h2>

<p>
    The Education App is designed to streamline the management of educational entities such as courses, departments, instructors, and trainees.
    Our mission is to provide an intuitive and efficient platform for educational institutions to handle their administrative tasks with ease.
</p>

<h3>Our Features</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Manage Courses: Create, edit, and delete courses with ease.</li>
    <li>Manage Departments: Organize courses under various departments.</li>
    <li>Manage Instructors: Assign instructors to courses and departments.</li>
    <li>Manage Trainees: Enroll trainees in courses and track their progress.</li>
</ul>

<p>
    We are committed to enhancing the educational experience through robust and user-friendly software solutions.
</p>
